"""Test that we conform to PEP-8."""
ignore_these_for_now = ['E111', 'E116', 'E121', 'E123', 'E126', 'E127',
    'E128', 'E203', 'E225', 'E226', 'E231', 'E251', 'E261', 'E265', 'E266',
    'E301', 'E302', 'E303', 'E305', 'E501', 'W391', 'W292', 'W293']
style = pycodestyle.StyleGuide(quiet=False, ignore=ignore_these_for_now)
style.input_dir('.')
result = style.check_files()
self.assertEqual(result.total_errors, 0,
    'Found code style errors (and warnings).')
